    <title>The History of the Confederation</title>
    <chapter>
        <title>Brief Description</title>
        <para>
        The Confederation of Systems, more commonly known as the 
        Confederation or Confed, is a collection of solar systems and colonies banded 
        together for both defense and trade. There has been a concerted 
        effort by the Confed to limit interference in the internal workings of the 
        actual systems.
        </para>
        <para>
        The Confed emcompasses a number of major racial groups. The Terrans 
        and the various derivative races of {\it Homo Terra Prime} 
        constitute a major portion of the current population. The Alpha 
        Centaurans and the derivative races of {\it Homo Alpha Centauran 
        Prime} constitute the next largest group followed closely by the 
        Proximans {\it Homo Proxima Prime}. There are no other known races 
        currently members of the Confed.
        </para>
        <para>
        The duties of the Confederation as a governing body are quite simple: 
        keep the peace {\em Between member systems}. To this end each system 
        donates a portion of its military services to the Confed as well as 
        some monetary support.
        </para>
    </chapter>

